一戦闘だけ敵の攻撃を完全に回避する。
Entry.EnglishText: Completely evades an enemy's attack for once.

Entry.EnglishText: Obtained funds are doubled for the next battle encounter.

Entry.JapaneseText: 次の戦闘で得られる経験値が２倍になる。
Entry.EnglishText: Obtained EXP is doubled for the next battle encounter.

Entry.JapaneseText: 敵にとどめを刺さずに、ＨＰを１０だけ残す。 自分より技量の低い相手にのみ有効。
Entry.EnglishText: A fatal attack will only leave the enemy at 10 HP. Only works when the opponent has a lower Skill stat than the caster.

Entry.JapaneseText: マップ兵器及び射程１以外の武器の射程が＋２。
Entry.EnglishText: +2 attack range, aside from MAP attacks and range 1 attacks.

Entry.EnglishText: Ignores damage reduction due to size difference, squadron formations, or Special Abilites and Special Skills.

Entry.EnglishText: +2 movement range to squadron for once.

Entry.JapaneseText: 一度だけ小隊移動力を＋４。 移動するまで効果は継続。
Entry.EnglishText: +4 movement range for squadron for once.

Entry.EnglishText: +1 action count for squadron. Cannot stack.

Entry.EnglishText: Restores 50% HP for all ally units on the map.
